my knee&mdash;My deare&s;t life&mdash;and made a very fine &s;peech on pre&s;enting the captain to her. No title, my&s;elf, to her lip or cheek, 'tis well he attempted not either&mdash;He was indeed ready to wor&s;hip her;&mdash;could only touch her charming hand&mdash;</P>
